    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You’ve obtained or crafted a special visor that helps hone your magical sight. This lens can be worn directly over your eyes or incorporated into any suit of armor. The visor appears devoid of eyeholes but doesn't obscure your vision. When worn, this visor grants you a +2 insight bonus to saving throws against visual effects. As a result of your training to improve your defenses, you also gain @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.zxBtaClmQw38z7LS]{proficiency with heavy armor}. If you’re already proficient with heavy armor, you instead gain @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.cloPjyXmg0zrvKaR]{proficiency with shields}. If you’re already proficient with shields, you instead gain the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.M5bWyOJchBhLAV1s]{Shield Block feat}.</p>"
